data.description: Nice family home w/4 bedrooms and large yard in quiet neighborhood!  Home is all brick for easy outdoor maintenance.  Double pane windows to help with lower utility bills.  Two bedrooms down and two up for the teens or craft/office space!  Dry basement w/laundry area and lots of storage space.  Bsmt. also has thick stone walls in excellent condition and could be finished for extra living space or work out area!  One car gar. w/newer gar. door.  Home has new int. paint, flooring, vanity, lighting and fresh painted cabinets, counter top and backsplash!  Perfect place to call home!
